Package clay.filter

The package containing Filters that can be used to filter CSVInput.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Filter
    An interface that describes a filter through which each data cell will be passed.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ExcludeColumnFilter
    A filter that will exclude certain columns from the CSV input.
    ExcludeColumnRangeFilter
    A filter that will exclude certain range of columns from the CSV input.
    ExcludeRowFilter
    A filter that will exclude certain rows from the CSV input.
    ExcludeRowRangeFilter
    A filter that will exclude certain range of rows from the CSV input.
    TrimFilter
    A filter that trims all leading and trailing spaces from a cell value.

Package clay.filter Description

The package containing Filters that can be used to filter CSVInput.
